    <div class="text-5xl font-bold">I'm Alexander Da Costa</div>
    <div class="text-3xl py-3 font-bold">Software Engineer and Web Developer</div>
    <div class="py-2">
      <text class="text-lg">
        <p>Greetings! I am a driven and inventive developer, eager to solve challenging business problems with systematic, innovative solutions. With a strong track record in digital transformation and a passion for learning new technologies, I aim to drive growth through technical expertise and creative problem-solving.</p><br>
        <p class="font-bold">Letâ€™s connect to discuss how my skills align with your organization's goals.</p>
      </text>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8">
      <a class="btn btn-outline ml" href="mailto:alexander.a.dacosta@gmail.com" target="_blank"> Let's connect!</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold mb-2">My last projects {"</>"}</div>
  </div>

  <HorizontalCard
    title="Muttly"
    img="/muttly_project_profile.webp"
    desc='Muttly is a fun web app that uses AI to creatively combine two dog breeds into a custom "Mutt," allowing users to generate, save, and share unique dog stats cards.'
    url="/blog/muttly-project-overview"
    badge="NEW"
  />
  <div class="divider my-0"></div>
  <HorizontalCard
    title="Boolebots"
    img="/boolebots_project_profile.webp"
